reviewText: WHEN ITS AVAILABLE LET ME KNOW CAUSE ITS A WINNER....this kids rich now, hes a sailor...WE GET THIS GUY LAID AND OUR TROUBLES ARE OVER..........GARRY HIXON

I think, for a TV movie, they did an excellent job in recreating the true story of little Jessica when she
fell in the well. Well acted and even though I knew the outcome I enjoyed seeing how they got there.
